skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sammy's kitchen
des: By simply asking Sammy's kitchen a question, you can hear all about what your favorite dining hall is serving for breakfast, lunch, dinner, and even late night! It has never been easier to get information about the food available at your local dining halls.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
